Miss Chu is well aware of that.

114
00:05:07,130 --> 00:05:08,020
General Cheng.

115
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,270
Are you

116
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,620
calling her a suspect?

117
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,110
Yes, Cheng Yuan.

118
00:05:14,350 --> 00:05:15,500
It could be anyone,

119
00:05:15,660 --> 00:05:17,220
but certainly not Miss Chu.

120
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,350
You know

121
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:21,740
if it was her or not.

122
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,580
Your Highness, this is serious.

123
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:24,200
Enough!

124
00:05:25,890 --> 00:05:26,800
This matter

125
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,740
is no longer your concern.

126
00:05:28,710 --> 00:05:29,560
You may leave.

127
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,150
Aye.

128
00:05:31,150 --> 00:05:31,590
Aye.

