144
00:06:21,990 --> 00:06:23,150
with war?

145
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:26,150
There’s a price

146
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:27,870
for everything.

147
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,440
And peace

148
00:06:32,910 --> 00:06:34,600
