170
00:07:59,110 --> 00:08:00,700
no longer take him seriously.

171
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,620
Who are you?

172
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:22,980
I am Yuan Chun,

173
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,860
your sister.

174
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,680
Can you play with me?

175
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,580
Sure.

176
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,950
From now on,

177
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:32,000
we can play together every day.

178
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:35,730
Are you happy?

179
00:08:35,730 --> 00:08:36,530
Yes.

180
00:08:36,680 --> 00:08:38,240
Let’s play then.

181
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:38,950
