182
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,580
I am going to kick it.

183
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,370
Yang.

184
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:50,670
No.

185
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:52,420
Yang.

186
00:08:55,590 --> 00:08:56,590
Who am I?

187
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,090
Sister!

188
00:08:58,090 --> 00:08:59,820
Are you sure?

189
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:00,640
Yes!

190
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:01,670
Really?

191
00:09:02,170 --> 00:09:02,810
Yes.

192
00:09:02,810 --> 00:09:03,640
See for yourself.

193
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:04,850
Are you correct?

194
00:09:06,930 --> 00:09:07,950
Are you?

195
00:09:07,950 --> 00:09:10,090
