210
00:09:43,310 --> 00:09:44,490
you recognized me instantly?

211
00:09:45,380 --> 00:09:47,030
Your fingers gave you away.

212
00:09:47,030 --> 00:09:48,440
You are so smart.

213
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:49,950
