214
00:09:50,470 --> 00:09:51,930
His Majesty invites Prince Yang

215
00:09:51,930 --> 00:09:54,030
to dine in Concubine Lan’s palace.

216
00:09:57,300 --> 00:09:58,030
I see.

217
00:10:00,110 --> 00:10:01,430
But Mr. Wang,

218
00:10:01,430 --> 00:10:03,230
he needs to wash his hands

219
00:10:03,230 --> 00:10:04,870
after playing with us.

220
