243
00:11:24,890 --> 00:11:27,930
Yuan Yang is a good boy.

244
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,590
His mother is gone.

245
00:11:30,980 --> 00:11:33,450
And I’m too busy

246
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:36,100
to look after him.

247
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:37,980
Why don’t you

248
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:40,730
adopt him

249
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:42,480
to take care of him?

250
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:45,900
That way, you can rely
on him in the future.

251
00:11:45,900 --> 00:11:47,220
What do you think?

252
00:11:50,010 --> 00:11:52,970
Thank you for your trust.

253
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,320
I will treat him

254
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,450
as my own

255
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:57,620
and take good care of him.

256
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:02,220
Your Majesty, Your Grace.

257
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:03,480
Prince Yang is here.

258
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,390
Father.

259
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,690
Yuan Yang.

260
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,740
Come here.

261
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:15,730
Father, are you feeling better?

262
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:18,480
I know you’re worried about me.

263
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,860
How could I not feel better?

264
00:12:24,830 --> 00:12:27,000
