265
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,360
Have some soup.

266
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:30,220
No.

267
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:32,240
I don’t want to be that rabbit.

268
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,480
What rabbit? Don’t be silly.

269
