00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:58,180
You won’t be a rabbit.

282
00:12:58,180 --> 00:13:00,340
Don’t be afraid.

283
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:02,190
Nothing will happen to you.

284
00:13:03,290 --> 00:13:04,960
Nothing at all.

