00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:11,070
Tell me.

288
00:13:12,850 --> 00:13:14,770
Who would you like to look after you?

289
00:13:31,050 --> 00:13:32,290
Dear Young Master Yue,

290
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:35,220
