I’ll pose a threat to his reign

296
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,930
if he makes me his heir.

297
00:13:50,460 --> 00:13:52,470
Therefore, he’s taking

298
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:53,550
more precautions against me.

299
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,680
His health is

300
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,120
falling off day by day.

301
00:13:58,620 --> 00:13:59,710
Recently,

302
00:13:59,710 --> 00:14:01,220
he intends to make his young son,

303
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:02,150
Yuan Yang, his heir

304
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:04,370
to protect his throne.

305
00:14:05,610 --> 00:14:07,070
Obviously, Yuan Chun

306
00:14:07,070 --> 00:14:08,050
saw through that

307
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,720
and deliberately approached Yuan Yang.

308
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:11,100
She alienated him

309
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,590
from Concubine Lan

310
00:14:12,590 --> 00:14:13,540
on purpose.

311
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:16,270
So Father had to ask her

312
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:18,130
to take care of Yuan Yang for now.

313
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,730
The power struggle has already begun.

314
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:24,860
Yuan Chun’s motive is obvious.

315
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:27,230
Now, Father is suspicious about me.

316
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,910
Yuan Chun also sees me

317
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:29,740
as a thorn in her flesh.

318
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:32,030
I am treading on thin ice.

319
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:34,620
The slightest mistake may bury me.

320
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:50,910
Prince Xiang,

321
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:53,560
it’s better to get away from danger.

322
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:55,830
Why don’t you volunteer

323
00:14:55,830 --> 00:14:57,160
to battle in Yanbei

324
00:14:57,550 --> 00:14:59,170
to fool Yuan Chun

325
00:15:00,010 --> 00:15:02,890
but hide outside Chang’an instead?

326
00:15:03,890 --> 00:15:05,420
Even if she takes action,

327
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:08,190
you can go back in time

328
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:09,300
to control the situation.

329
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:21,700
Sister,

330
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,620
why is brother

331
00:15:23,620 --> 00:15:24,590
leaving?

332
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:30,170
Well,

333
00:15:32,780 --> 00:15:34,290
isn’t it good?

334
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:18,920
Wang.

335
00:16:20,410 --> 00:16:21,790
Servant.

336
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:26,290
Lan.

337
00:16:30,580 --> 00:16:31,880
Lan.

338
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,400
Somebody.

339
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,310
Bring me the medicine.

340
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,450
I need to take it.

341
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:45,660
Chun, there you are.

342
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:49,310
Give me the medicine.

343
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:51,700
Father, do you want this?

344
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:59,560
It’s too hot. You can take it later.

345
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:07,410
Where are Lan and Chief Eunuch Wang?

346
00:18:08,500 --> 00:18:10,980
Where are the others?

347
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:13,790
I asked them to leave

348
00:18:13,910 --> 00:18:15,410
because they failed to serve you well.

349
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:17,970
You are sick, Father.

350
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:19,620
You should have a good rest.

351
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:22,450
I will keep you company. Aren’t you happy?

352
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:31,980
What do you want?

353
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,910
Nothing.

354
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,280
I just want to talk to you.

355
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,430
There’re just you and me

356
00:18:41,330 --> 00:18:43,430
in this room.

357
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,830
No one else is here.

358
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,720
We won’t be disturbed.

359
00:18:53,320 --> 00:18:57,020
Father, I have always

360
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,690
wanted to ask you about something

361
00:18:58,990 --> 00:19:00,670
but never got the chance to.

362
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:07,460
Back then, when you

363
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,460
married me to Yan Xun,

364
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:11,470
was I a bait to you?

365
00:19:15,470 --> 00:19:19,160
I had no choice.

366
00:19:21,090 --> 00:19:22,160
The only thing I regret

367
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:25,820
is that I didn’t kill that traitor.

368
00:19:37,150 --> 00:19:38,880
The happiest moment

369
00:19:38,880 --> 00:19:39,870
in my life was

370
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,070
when you approved

371
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:44,340
our marriage.

372
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:47,180
But in the end,

373
00:19:47,940 --> 00:19:50,260
that was nothing but a sham.

374
00:19:51,340 --> 00:19:55,420
A lie from the very beginning.

375
00:19:58,580 --> 00:20:00,750
Yan Xun’s sin

376
00:20:01,430 --> 00:20:03,480
can’t be forgiven

377
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:05,510
even if he is torn into pieces.

378
00:20:06,700 --> 00:20:10,430
Why are you so obsessed with him?

379
00:20:11,090 --> 00:20:12,370
He is my childhood sweetheart.

380
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:13,930
We grew up together.

381
00:20:15,690 --> 00:20:17,330
I love him.

382
00:20:17,330 --> 00:20:19,620
I’ve loved him since long ago.

383
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:22,720
I thought you knew that.

384
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:27,040
Chun, you don’t know his true color.

385
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,070
You were fooled by him.

386
00:20:29,070 --> 00:20:30,350
I wasn’t.

387
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:33,320
He had stayed in Chang’an for years

388
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:35,040
without causing any trouble.

389
00:20:35,040 --> 00:20:36,660
He was always sweet to me.

390
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:39,190
Hadn’t you…

391
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,930
Hadn’t you suspected your sworn brother,

392
00:20:42,210 --> 00:20:44,490
massacred his people,
slaughtered his clan,

393
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:45,510
tortured Yan Xun

394
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,130
on the Jiuyou Platform,

395
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:48,230
in the cruelest way,

396
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:49,710
how would he have rebelled

397
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:50,820
against you?

398
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:54,150
Just like his father,

399
00:20:54,740 --> 00:20:56,450
he’s disloyal.

400
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:59,320
He’s rising in rebellion,

401
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:01,740
plunging the people
into misery and suffering.

402
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:03,900
It’s you who’s making them suffer!

403
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:06,190
It is you who should be punished!

404
00:21:06,190 --> 00:21:07,830
It is you who must go to hell!

405
00:21:07,830 --> 00:21:08,830
Enough!

406
00:21:09,990 --> 00:21:11,980
How dare you slander your father

407
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:15,000
for a traitor?

408
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,060
Father?

409
00:21:21,090 --> 00:21:22,620
Now, you know

410
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:24,460
you are a father.

411
00:21:27,740 --> 00:21:29,120
I used to think that

412
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,330
you were like

413
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:32,060
every father in the world.

414
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:34,660
You would think for your children.

415
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,940
I never anticipated that

416
00:21:37,470 --> 00:21:38,400
I...

417
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:41,020
I was merely a pawn in your plan.

418
00:21:41,630 --> 00:21:43,260
When you used me

419
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:45,840
to kill Yan Xun,

420
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,060
did it ever occur to you

421
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,080
that you

422
00:21:48,080 --> 00:21:49,120
were a father?

423
00:21:51,730 --> 00:21:52,930
Do you know how many sins

424
00:21:52,930 --> 00:21:54,990
you have committed throughout your life?

425
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:57,740
You killed Marquis Dingbei
who was innocent.

426
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,030
You left Bai Sheng no choice
but to kill herself.

427
00:21:59,030 --> 00:22:01,080
Persecuting the loyal is your first sin.

428
00:22:01,790 --> 00:22:03,350
Branding Yanbei people as rebels,

429
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:04,840
and massacring innocent people

430
00:22:04,840 --> 00:22:05,950
are your second sin.

431
00:22:06,440 --> 00:22:07,530
To keep people from

432
00:22:07,530 --> 00:22:08,510
calling you a tyrant,

433
00:22:08,510 --> 00:22:09,860
you deliberately spared

434
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:10,550
Yan Xun’s life.

435
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:13,090
But you incited noble families in secret

436
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:13,610
to assassinate him,

437
00:22:13,610 --> 00:22:15,170
turning them against each other

438
00:22:15,350 --> 00:22:16,790
for your benefit.

439
00:22:16,790 --> 00:22:18,010
That’s your third sin.

440
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:21,360
My mother, Noble Consort Wei,

441
00:22:21,690 --> 00:22:23,210
was with you for decades.

442
00:22:23,870 --> 00:22:25,580
Yet you made her poison herself to death

443
00:22:25,580 --> 00:22:27,260
despite your marriage.

444
00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:29,610
And Yuan Song, my brother,

445
00:22:30,450 --> 00:22:33,210
he’s never wanted anything

446
00:22:33,210 --> 00:22:34,620
but you exiled him.

447
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:37,110
Yuan Che has great ambitions.

448
00:22:37,110 --> 00:22:38,230
But you’d rather

449
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:39,050
pick an ignorant child

450
00:22:39,050 --> 00:22:40,380
to accede

451
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:40,920
to the throne

452
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:42,580
in fear of losing your power!

453
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,480
Do you want me to continue?

454
00:22:58,170 --> 00:23:01,250
You are a merciless emperor,

455
00:23:01,410 --> 00:23:03,990
a disloyal brother, a heartless father

456
00:23:04,300 --> 00:23:05,640
and a suspicious, jealous

457
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,720
spineless coward!

458
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:08,850
That’s why you ended up

459
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:10,820
all alone like this.

460
00:23:19,730 --> 00:23:20,790
Father.

461
00:23:22,970 --> 00:23:24,720
Let me tell you one thing.

462
00:23:26,740 --> 00:23:29,660
Either you let others live,

463
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:31,650
or eradicate their entire clan.

464
00:23:32,890 --> 00:23:34,760
When you murdered Marquis Dingbei,

465
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,990
you should have murdered Yan Xun, too.

466
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:39,400
When you killed my mother,

467
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:42,770
you should have killed me, too.

468
00:23:53,810 --> 00:23:55,740
You weren’t like this before.

469
00:23:59,100 --> 00:24:00,700
You used to be...

470
00:24:02,580 --> 00:24:03,590
Used to be...

471
00:24:05,180 --> 00:24:07,550
Different.

472
00:24:14,230 --> 00:24:15,880
That’s because I know

473
00:24:16,650 --> 00:24:19,510
good people always get bullied

474
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:22,860
and the innocent always die first.

475
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,230
It’s not that I have changed,

476
00:24:26,490 --> 00:24:28,380
but I have grown up.

477
00:24:33,030 --> 00:24:34,730
I didn’t want to be a princess.

478
00:24:35,380 --> 00:24:36,680
I didn’t want

479
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,790
fame or wealth.

480
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:39,500
All I wanted

481
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:41,950
was to live with my love

482
00:24:41,950 --> 00:24:43,210
for the rest of my life.

483
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:45,390
But now,

484
00:24:47,300 --> 00:24:52,000
my mother died, my brother left,

485
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:55,640
and my love abandoned me.

486
00:24:57,460 --> 00:24:58,480
People I care about

487
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,420
have left one by one.

488
00:25:01,650 --> 00:25:04,080
Now, I’m the only one left.

489
00:25:06,210 --> 00:25:07,670
Do you know

490
00:25:07,670 --> 00:25:09,760
that I have nightmares every night?

491
00:25:09,950 --> 00:25:11,540
I wish I were dead!

492
00:25:18,580 --> 00:25:19,450
Never mind.

493
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,620
How could I expect

494
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:26,010
the most selfish one in the world

495
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,980
to understand my feelings?

496
00:25:32,330 --> 00:25:33,670
What are you doing?

497
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,300
What is that?

498
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,880
Chun, what are you doing?

499
00:25:58,700 --> 00:25:59,550
Chun.

500
00:26:02,020 --> 00:26:03,010
What is that?

501
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:20,450
What are you doing?

502
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:22,990
Help!

503
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:26,060
Help!

504
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:28,270
Somebody help!

505
00:26:28,620 --> 00:26:29,960
Help!

506
00:26:31,230 --> 00:26:32,900
- Help!
- Stop barking.

507
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:34,360
- It’s useless.
- Help!

508
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:41,080
I almost drowned by accident when I was 8,

509
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:42,780
then I had a high fever.

510
00:26:43,130 --> 00:26:45,530
You took care of me tirelessly

511
00:26:46,060 --> 00:26:47,890
and had all the ponds

512
00:26:47,890 --> 00:26:48,890
in the palace filled up.

513
00:26:50,540 --> 00:26:52,030
Who would expect

514
00:26:52,410 --> 00:26:54,170
that you and I

515
00:26:54,170 --> 00:26:55,620
would turn against each other now?

516
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,580
I wasn’t cruel

517
00:26:59,470 --> 00:27:01,230
or shrewd enough.

518
00:27:02,690 --> 00:27:04,980
It was you who made me come this far

519
00:27:06,770 --> 00:27:08,440
step by step.

520
00:27:13,180 --> 00:27:16,300
Father, it’s time to take your medicine.

521
00:27:21,700 --> 00:27:23,540
You are committing murder and regicide!

522
00:27:24,730 --> 00:27:26,440
I will give the throne to Yuan Yang

523
00:27:27,290 --> 00:27:29,230
as you wish.

524
00:27:29,580 --> 00:27:32,670
But I will be assisting him.

525
00:27:33,820 --> 00:27:36,470
Chun, I know I was wrong.

526
00:27:36,580 --> 00:27:37,740
You can take my place.

527
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:39,560
I will give it to you, alright?

528
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:42,290
Why would I need that?

529
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:44,300
What I want

530
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:48,550
has already been destroyed by you.

531
00:27:51,530 --> 00:27:54,220
Be good and take this.

532
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:56,120
Finish it and get some rest.

533
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:07,240
Stop.

534
00:28:09,130 --> 00:28:10,050
Help!

535
00:28:10,990 --> 00:28:12,060
Help!

536
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,250
Why are you back?

537
00:28:14,710 --> 00:28:17,450
Chun, you went too far this time.

538
00:28:17,610 --> 00:28:18,940
I understand you hold a grudge,

539
00:28:18,940 --> 00:28:20,450
but you’re committing a heinous crime.

540
00:28:20,450 --> 00:28:21,870
A heinous crime?

541
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:24,150
What he did

542
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:25,430
is tens of thousands of times

543
00:28:25,430 --> 00:28:26,790
worse than me.

544
00:28:26,790 --> 00:28:28,400
He is our father after all.

545
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,290
Father?

546
00:28:29,660 --> 00:28:31,320
Did he act as a father

547
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,760
when he married me to Yan Xun?

548
00:28:32,760 --> 00:28:33,920
Did he act as a father

549
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,300
when he killed my mother?

550
00:28:35,300 --> 00:28:36,410
Did he act as a father

551
00:28:36,410 --> 00:28:38,270
when he kicked you out of the city?

552
00:28:39,060 --> 00:28:40,600
What he did to us is unforgivable.

553
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:42,890
Why should I still be kind to him?

554
00:28:43,050 --> 00:28:44,180
I must kill him!

555
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:44,620
Chun!

556
00:28:44,620 --> 00:28:45,700
- I must kill him!
- Chun!

557
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:46,830
Stop!

558
00:28:54,410 --> 00:28:55,450
Whatever it takes,

559
00:28:56,130 --> 00:28:57,970
I cannot let you do it!

560
00:29:03,870 --> 00:29:04,710
Father.

561
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:00,070
Are you sure it’s true?

562
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:00,900
Absolutely.

563
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:01,940
I saw it with my own eyes

564
00:30:01,940 --> 00:30:03,410
that Princess had been
sent out of the palace.

565
00:30:03,730 --> 00:30:04,730
What to do?

566
00:30:05,670 --> 00:30:06,710
What should we do now?

567
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,150
His Majesty

568
00:30:08,530 --> 00:30:09,810
won’t let her get away with it.

569
00:30:09,810 --> 00:30:11,650
No. I can’t let it happen.

570
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,140
I must save her.

571
00:30:13,690 --> 00:30:14,480
Young Master. Young Master.

572
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:14,920
What are you doing?

573
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:15,760
I’m going to save her.

574
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:16,780
Are you going to rebel, Young Master?

575
00:30:16,780 --> 00:30:17,750
I’m going to save Princess.

576
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:18,900
Why would I rebel?

577
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:20,140
Disobeying orders is an act of rebellion.

578
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:20,400
Young Master.

579
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:21,470
Whatever! The situation is dire!

580
00:30:21,470 --> 00:30:22,320
Young Master!

581
00:30:22,450 --> 00:30:23,240
Young Master!

582
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:46,260
Yuwen Yue.

583
00:30:47,280 --> 00:30:48,710
Thanks to your idea,

584
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:51,130
I made an excuse to leave Chang’an

585
00:30:51,130 --> 00:30:52,510
and stationed the troops outside the city,

