00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:56,750
I followed Father’s order

671
00:35:56,750 --> 00:35:57,900
and came to Yanbei.

672
00:35:58,880 --> 00:35:59,840
I thought

673
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:00,970
