674
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:04,100
and Chun would

675
00:36:04,100 --> 00:36:04,990
be herself again.

676
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,340
Your Highness.

677
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,780
Please wait here for me.

678
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:33,230
Your Highness, look.

679
00:36:35,680 --> 00:36:36,710
When I was a kid,

680
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:38,060
I was good at making this.

681
00:36:38,580 --> 00:36:39,900
Everyone in the village

682
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:41,470
came to me for help.

683
00:36:43,060 --> 00:36:44,410
There was a time

684
00:36:44,410 --> 00:36:46,040
when scarecrows I made

685
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:47,570
were all over the fields in our village.

686
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:52,040
You must be a smart girl

687
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,030
when you were a kid.

688
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,100
Your neighbors

689
00:36:55,100 --> 00:36:56,350
