694
00:37:07,130 --> 00:37:08,130
Did they...

695
00:37:09,900 --> 00:37:10,820
They all died.

696
00:37:12,930 --> 00:37:13,930
I was making scarecrows

697
00:37:13,930 --> 00:37:14,980
in the field

